{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><div data-type=\"info\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u30155e5d\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">重点提示：</span></strong></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ua203333e\"><span class=\"ne-text\">「排版风格」、「超宽显示」、文档信息等功能搬迁到右上角「...」里</span></li><li id=\"ud4880382\"><span class=\"ne-text\">取消保存按钮；在编辑过程中，系统会自动保存编辑内容，你也可以使用键盘上的 ctrl/ command +S 快速保存</span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u746cf7db\"><span class=\"ne-text\">「标签功能」搬迁到右上角「...」-文档设置中</span></li><li id=\"u630bace2\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在编辑和阅读模式下，若想要展示更多内容，将鼠标悬浮在表格上方，在弹出菜单栏中点击</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553783402-52818cd7-9420-4bef-9935-5c8732af13d4.png\" width=\"25\" id=\"ue5de62a2\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮，即可将表格设为「全宽展示」。</span></li></ul></div><p id=\"u9ba641a7\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"QHfJG\"><span class=\"ne-text\">常见问题</span></h2><h4 id=\"wlcuf\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">1、</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">怎么更改页面宽度？</span></h4><p id=\"u444c96c9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">升级后，页面布局有了新变化，去除了纸张的页面布局，整体正文内容会居中显示。</span></p><p id=\"u757d5392\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">若想更改页面宽度，点击右上角「...」图标，即可开启</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">「超宽模式」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">进行超宽展示效果。</span></p><h4 id=\"CUaHj\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553853873-ecfcb435-36ba-4d55-9297-9e80910f9811.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"LxrHl\" class=\"ne-image\"></h4><h4 id=\"wtdZ3\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">2、</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">怎么设置排版风格？</span></h4><p id=\"u04878b3e\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">点击右上角「...」图标，即可设置排版风格。</span></p><p id=\"u1121084c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553834183-768a1c95-0e9b-4e95-8f8a-f5de702740f0.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"vBgOS\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"auiO2\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">3、没有保存按钮了，担心我的文档内容没有保存？</span></h4><p id=\"uc436a8c9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1)\">在编辑过程中，系统会自动保存内容。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1)\">另外，支持使用</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\"> Ctrl (或command） + s</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1)\">快捷键，会触发手动保存。</span></p><p id=\"u18de5fdf\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1)\"></span></p><h4 id=\"trYNM\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">4、怎么更改文档信息？</span></h4><p id=\"uc0f2a6f8\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">点击右上角「...」-「文档设置」，即可更改文档摘录、路径等。</span></p><p id=\"uabe950e4\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553883036-08db7861-1331-4387-8c9f-e81708f4e6a4.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"u092abc5c\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uc8adde11\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553948832-358d7331-01d7-4141-be68-a5145ff1ab6d.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"u8dc11661\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"y0y28\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">5、文档的标签功能去哪里了？</span></h4><p id=\"u65de538c\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">点击右上角「...」-</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">「文档设置」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">，下拉到面板下方即可看到。<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553976451-9ea2704c-82de-4fd7-94a2-5ae738a64927.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"u62397719\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"gBpBP\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">6、如何查看统计信息（字数统计、编辑者和创建时间）？</span></h4><p id=\"uac693bc2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">点击右上角「...」可在，面板最下方看到字数统计、创建时间、最后编辑时间和编辑者。</span></p><p id=\"ued355f83\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553994627-c5f6085f-5f38-436f-81a7-4da691ac620d.png\" width=\"929.3333333333334\" id=\"ub5bceff1\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"NGVLd\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">7、插入卡片功能介绍</span></h4><p id=\"u3d3f5ff9\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">插入卡片功能在原有基础上新增了</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">「最近使用」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">，会将你近期使用过的卡片功能收录在这一板块，最多展示4个。</span></p><p id=\"uf849ce98\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553818906-a49aabc3-cfd3-4d56-95ff-8e00ff56514b.png\" width=\"854\" id=\"udcd488a0\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u307a99c5\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">如果找不到“引入”模块，请在唤起插入卡片后向下移动或鼠标滚动向下，直到出现“引入”模块为止。</span></p><p id=\"uec20d5fc\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\"></span></p><p id=\"u5f629d24\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">另外在正文行首输入快捷键</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">「 / 」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">或者行内</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">「command + /」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #262626\">，即可快速唤起面板，使用语雀特色卡片及格式</span></p><p id=\"uf12068d5\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\"></span></p><p id=\"udd72094e\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635483454682-cd5d0b7a-3190-4382-8883-05709bd7d4ec.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"u125252d2\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u050e6e8f\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u10c7c00c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">同时输入快捷键「/」后，还支持直接搜索中文，拼音，拼音首字母，英文，直接在菜单面板中定位匹配。</span></p><p id=\"ue3c97bcf\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ucc741438\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">中文：</span></strong></p><p id=\"u404b5b25\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635483650675-1000a8c8-fdb8-4c08-9ba5-a8e58777445c.png\" width=\"803\" id=\"ua2c2fcfb\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u563725f0\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">拼音：</span></strong></p><p id=\"u383efb3f\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635483650679-b8144099-b174-43cb-9859-f3ffffaaab51.png\" width=\"790\" id=\"ufa6e10ce\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uf27e5311\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u32c96e08\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">拼音首字母：</span></strong></p><p id=\"uae163c1f\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635483650773-659e51b2-5bc9-4bc9-a7c5-2636d9da60e4.png\" width=\"816\" id=\"u850e9b5b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ueac82a30\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">英文：</span></strong></p><p id=\"ud9c65077\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635483650713-bcd2ee1f-4b2f-462a-89f3-9cf4d9fec9f0.png\" width=\"817\" id=\"uce55d70f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"Zlvui\"><span class=\"ne-text\">8、编辑完后，我想快速返回到知识库首页如何操作？</span></h4><p id=\"u5ef2bb29\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以点击左上角导航栏中，文档标题下方的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">「知识库标题」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，快速跳转回知识库首页。<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553819173-c52ad249-c07b-4233-862b-142d9d58d3d5.png\" width=\"1389\" id=\"KWwzf\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uc1d455f3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"psVpo\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">9、工具栏没有大纲按钮了，如何快速打开、关闭大纲？</span></h4><p id=\"u1555adf2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">将鼠标悬浮在大纲上，可快速唤起图钉按钮，点击图钉即可</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">「钉住大纲」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">，将大纲在右侧固定展示；再次点击即可</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">「隐藏大纲」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">，将大纲收缩在最右侧中间位置，呈现mini状态，为大家留出更大空间进行创作。</span></p><p id=\"udca2ebfa\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/gif/21674429/1635824786512-93560b7a-f9e5-4ea5-84ad-fd6a19d7738f.gif\" width=\"1361\" id=\"u8869886a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"wNVRa\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">10、上传图片后，如何进行图片设置？</span></h4><p id=\"ub1f4139d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">在新版文档编辑器中，成功上传图片后，点击图片右侧不会直接弹出</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">「图片设置」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">面板。<br />为方便大家操作，我们新增了工具栏菜单，你可以将鼠标悬浮在图片上，在弹出的工具栏中菜单中直接设置</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">图片对齐方式、图片样式、调节图片大小、</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">将文档内图片直接</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">保存到资源知识库</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1); background-color: #FFFFFF\">。</span></p><p id=\"u3b42f62e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"><br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635823642330-9b6a4c07-e003-4886-b782-ef0f57b69849.png\" width=\"614.6666666666666\" id=\"u5562a5a1\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ue4c279bc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">同时，如果想进入图片编辑面板，可以点击</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635823688074-926e37b1-4cad-4b52-8f6a-f6e533bc7c38.png\" width=\"18\" id=\"u53e631e2\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮，即可在右侧弹出图片设置面板。</span></p><p id=\"u0a99b8e2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1635823727881-63a69b5e-a3ed-4dbe-9c3e-8e36ef12ef6e.png\" width=\"784.6666666666666\" id=\"ufc63a692\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u571d8143\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"c6dQe\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #404040; background-color: #FFFFFF\">11、如何将表格设置为全宽阅读？</span></h4><p id=\"u476dcf31\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">在编辑和阅读模式下，若想要展示更多内容，将鼠标悬浮在表格上方，在弹出菜单栏中点击按钮，即可将表格设为「全宽展示」。</span></p><p id=\"u16a8e9fd\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553819887-7a9601e9-94f4-457f-89ba-bcd471811b4c.png\" width=\"800\" id=\"u8c305333\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u0c92db1b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"CNGkM\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(22,21,21,1)\">12、新版本发布后，如何在阅读页面快速跳转到知识库所在的团队呢？</span></h4><p id=\"u91d8b970\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">出于想在阅读页面突出知识库的目的，我们在左上角仅显示本文档所在知识库标题，若想要快速跳转回该知识库所在团队/空间，可以点击</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">「左上角知识库标题」</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">回到知识库首页，点击左上角团队即可跳回。</span></p><p id=\"udad7fe14\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/gif/21674429/1634554331318-545860a4-28d1-4e03-9546-339ed238ff80.gif\" width=\"800\" id=\"ubfc93b8c\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u926feaf5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"wVKUn\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">13、可以退回以前的编辑器版本吗？</span></h4><p id=\"u4ede05cf\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">新文档升级后，目前不支持退回旧版，</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">非常抱歉。若在使用新版过程中遇到问题，可以将具体问题描述，填写在我们的新版反馈表单中。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">入口在文档右下角：</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634553820206-aa2ea9e3-3e95-4008-9a1b-696e7517e670.png\" width=\"120\" id=\"u9912fcf3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u0e8ea3a2\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"line-height: 2\"><br></p><h4 id=\"bRA44\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1)\">14、桌面端的菜单栏为什么不一致？</span></h4><p id=\"u9b51ac4f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">桌面端的更新已有计划，预计 11月 会更新到最新版本。</span></p><p id=\"u7a2934f5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"Afo62\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgba(27,27,27,1)\"></span></h4><p id=\"u577af99f\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></div>",
  "slug": 55481467,
  "title": "新文档编辑器常见问题"
}